  "title": "Bicycle Mechanic",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Perform repairs, tune-ups, and diagnostics on mechanical and e-bike systems to ensure safe and reliable operation.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assemble new mechnical bikes out of box</li><li>Diagnose mechanical and electrical issues on e-bikes to identify necessary repairs</li><li>Perform repairs on mechanical and electrical components to restore proper function</li><li>Conduct tune-ups to maintain optimal bike performance and safety</li><li>Test repaired bikes to confirm issues are resolved before returning to customers</li><li>Maintain a clean and organized work area to support efficient repair processes</li><li>Basic selling skills is a plus point</li></ul><p>Working Hours:</p><ul><li>11am to 7:30pm on Monday - Saturday, </li><li>All Sundays and Public Holidays off</li></ul>",
